Package: vagalumeR
Type: Package
Title: Access to the 'Vagalume' API
Version: 0.1.6
Author: Bruna Wundervald
Maintainer: Bruna Wundervald <brunadaviesw@gmail.com>
Description: Provides access to the 'Vagalume' API <https://api.vagalume.com.br>. 
    The data extracted is basically lyrics of songs and information about
    artists/bands.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.4)
Suggests:
    ggplot2,
    knitr,
    tm
URL: https://github.com/r-music/vagalumeR
BugReports: https://github.com/r-music/vagalumeR/issues
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Imports: jsonlite,
    httr,
    stringr,
    dplyr,
    purrr,
    magrittr
